As this demonic entity grows from the idea you came up with, he only grows stronger and undefeatable.
And the ones you loved and cared for...?
Barely remember who you used to be.
Because they believe in this monster that NOT ONLY TOOK YOUR LIFE,
but- your ever lasting legacy in this world.

I hope that since you’ve come this far in this story, that you think about your surroundings.
I hope that you begin to question what SEEMS like an impossible mistake...
...and that the person trying to wake you from this nightmare, IS TRYING TO SAVE YOUR LIFE.
And, not just your life...?
But, your spirit too.

Now, the final question that this story asks, is...
...do you feel alone there, in the uncanny valley...?
Because, the biggest assumption that you most likely made in this story...
...is that I took this adventure INTO, the uncanny valley WITH you.

Your assumptions are your worst enemy.
And they are... that demons best friend.

